                <head>103. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee (Intelligence)
                        Meeting<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d103fn1">Source: Carter Library,
                        Plains File, Subject File, Box 30, <gloss target="#t_NSC_1"
                            >NSC</gloss>/<gloss target="#t_SCC_1">SCC</gloss> Minutes,
                        3/1/80–4/15/80. Secret; Sensitive. The meeting took place in the White House
                        Situation Room.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            from="1980-04-07T15:30:00-05:00" to="1980-04-07T16:30:00-05:00">April 7,
                            1980, 3:30–4:30 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
